fields.name: call_park
fields.description: If you need to move to another place during a call, use this function.

fields.name: intercom
fields.description: Directly speak without answering the call.

fields.name: speed_dial
fields.description: Automatically call the specified number when key is pressed. (No BFL)

fields.name: voicemail
fields.description: You can press the key to listen to voice messages and configure the line. The LED is on if a new voice message is received.

fields.name: call_forward
fields.description: When receiving a call, you can press the key to transfer the call to the specified number.
